## The podcast trail

**Investigate** is the listening side of *Unschool Discoveries*.

This is where we slow down, follow the clues, and talk through the ideas hiding inside the stories — curiosity, family life, nature, creativity, learning, and the strange little questions that turn into bigger discoveries.

Each episode is a trail.  
Some trails begin in the book.  
Some begin in real life.  
Some lead straight into the living notebook.

