## What we investigate

The podcast explores the space between the story-world and the real world.

We may talk about:

- clues from the book
- behind-the-scenes story choices
- family adventures
- unschooling moments
- nature finds
- creative projects
- questions children ask
- discoveries that start small and grow bigger

